#- You nod politely and§0
§0move on with your§0
§0journey. It is fairly§0
§0dark so you use your§0
§0staff to cast a flame§0
§0spell. You set yourself§0
§0on fire on accident!§0
§0What a novice you are.§0
§0Do you take off your§0
§0clothes (Page 11) or§0
§0roll on the ground§0
§0(Page 36)§0

#- You attempt to flee but§0
§0you feel your body§0
§0being sucked§0
§0downward. What the§0
