§0Its lion jaws rip your§0
§0body to shreads.§0
§0
§4§lYou have died.§0

#- You strike the chimera§0
§0but your sword§0
§0shatters on impact.§0
§0You dodge a few blows§0
§0but the tail injects§0
§0venom into you. Your§0
§0body tightens up and§0
