#- The hard way huh?§0
§0The slime girl throws a bucket of slime onto you. It immediately starts to dissolve your flesh and you scream out in intense pain. Why did you think this was a good choice?§0
§0
§4§lYou have died.
#- You resist the slime§0
§0girl's charm. "No one§0
§0has ever resisted me§0
§0before. Let me reward§0
§0you with my pet." She§0
§0hands you a baby§0
§0sloth and it slumps§0
§0over your shoulder.§0
§0Do you accept this§0
§0strange gift (Page 28)§0
§0or reject the cute§0
§0sloth (Page 4).§0

#- You cant control§0
§0yourself and reach§0
§0for the music box§0
§0again. That eerie§0
§0melody is so soothing.§0
§0The old man flashes a§0
§0wide smile as you§0
§0continue to play the§0
§0music box. Again and§0
§0again. And again. And§0
§0again. Forever.§0
§0
§4§lYou have died.§0

#- You look around for a§0
§0way forward. While§0
§0searching, the lifeless§0
§0skeleton gets up and§0
§0takes your sword from§0
§0your belt. "I'm sorry§0
§0sir, I obey any§0
§0master" it announces§0
§0as it pierces your§0
§0chest from behind.§0
§0
§4§lYou have died.§0

#- You gaze into the§0
§0timestone but see§0
§0nothing. You feel a§0
§0swift wack to the back§0
§0of your head and fall§0
§0unconcious. Your body§0
§0gets dragged across§0
§0the tomb's decayed§0
§0floors. You wake up§0
§0and find yourself in a§0
