§0and the slime leaves§0
§0your ankle. As you do§0
§0so, seven more§0
§0tentacles wrap around§0
§0your legs and release§0
§0a deadly electrical§0
§0shock. The shocktopus§0
§0doesn't like intruders.§0
§0
§4§lYou have died.§0

#- You attempt to flee but§0
§0the man is too quick§0
§0for you. "You've made§0
§0a deal with the devil by§0
§0entering this tomb"§0
§0jeered Lucifer. "All§0
