§0
§4§lYou have died.§0

#- You examine the window§0
§0and manage to get it§0
§0open. You seem to be§0
§0really high up!§0
§0Underneath the window§0
§0ledge are some vines.§0
§0Far below you a great§0
§0distance away is a§0
§0large pile of hay. Do§0
