§0target your chest and§0
§0your heart swells up.§0
§0You go into cardiac§0
§0arrest and slump onto§0
§0the ground.§0
§0
§4§lYou have died.§0

#- You ignore the dog§0
§0and move on ahead. In§0
§0front of you is a§0
§0Chimera! You charge at§0
